CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 28, 1963, pg. 13, reads: "Glamorous Rinkydinks - Setting the Pittsburgh community back on its heels, recently, with a unique Sunday afternoon 'Showcase on Art,' were these members of the Rinkydinks.  Left to right: Beatrice Adams, Aileen Mellix, Georgia Simonson, who was chairman of the 'Showcase'; Rubye [Ruby] Young Buchanan, Gaye deHall, president; Gertna Horseley, Doryce Griffin Allen and Doris Summers. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of Rinkydinks Club, from left: Beatrice Adams, Aileen Mellix, Georgia Simonson, Ruby Young Buchanan, Gaye deHall, Gertna Horseley, Doryce Griffin Allen, and Doris Summers
